Package eu.su.mas.dedaleEtu.princ

Class Principal

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.su.mas.dedaleEtu.princ.Principal
  • public class Principal
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to start the platform and the agents. To launch your agents in the environment you desire you will have to :
    • set the ConfigurationFile parameters (and maybe update the files in resources/) ConfigurationFile
    • create your agents classes and call them in the createAgents method below
    Author:
    hc

        Parameters:
        containerName -
        host - is the IP of the host where the main-container should be listen to. A null value means use the default (i.e. localhost)
        platformID - is the symbolic name of the platform, if different from default. A null value means use the default (i.e. localhost)
        port - (if null, 8888 by default)
